# subscript(_:)

**Instance Subscript**

Returns the Virtio console port configuration as the specified index.

## Declaration

```swift
subscript(portIndex: Int) -> VZVirtioConsolePortConfiguration? { get set }
```

## Parameters

- **portIndex**: The index of the configuration to retrieve.

## Return Value

The [doc://com.apple.virtualization/documentation/Virtualization/VZVirtioConsolePortConfiguration], or nil is the index exceeds the number of configurations in the array.
